microstructure: BCC solid solution phase and particulates-reinforced phase MC-carbide
evidence: Mo 0.5 NbHf 0.5 ZrTiC 0.1 and Mo 0.5 NbHf 0.5 ZrTiC 0.3 alloys are composed of BCC solid solution phase and particulates-reinforced phase MC-carbide. MC carbide with FCC crystal structure is enriched with Zr and Hf and containing a small amount of Nb and Ti. Both the compressive strength and plasticity of Mo 0.5 NbHf 0.5 ZrTiC 0.1 and Mo 0.5 NbHf 0.5 ZrTiC 0.3 alloys are improved compared with the master alloy Mo 0.5 NbHf 0.5 ZrTi.
